\id 2TH Bible in Fouta-Jalon Pular 
\mt1 ∆ÅATAKURU PUULUSA ∆äIMMURU HAA E ∆ÅE TESALONII ∆ÅEN 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Immorde e an min Puulusa, wondude e Silaasi e Timotee, haa e ngal *moftal wongal Tesalonii humondirngal e Alla Baaba men, e Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi on:  
\v 2 yo mo∆¥∆¥ere e …ìuttu wonan on immorde e Alla Baaba men, e Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi on. 
\s1 Fii no Alla ∆ùaawiroyta Yim…ìe …ìen 
\p  
\v 3 Me…óen haani, yo musi…ì…ìe, duumaade e jarnugol Alla fii mon, …óun-le ko ko feewi, ko fii gom…óinal mon ngal no …ìeydaade, awa kadi giggol ngol yi…óindir…óon ngol ko e …ìeydaade tun woni.  
\v 4 E hoore …óun, me…óen mantorde on e nder mofte Alla …óen, sabu ≈ãa…≤…≤aare mon nden e gom…óinal mon ngal e nder cukkan…óe …óe cukka…óon …óen fow e satteendeeji …ói wakkili…óon …óin. 
\p  
\v 5 Awa, ko …óun…óoo woni seedee …≤aawoore Alla feewunde nden, fii no woniron rin…óan…ìe *laamu Alla ngu won…óon tampande ngun.  
\v 6 Ko fii no feewi yeeso Alla ka o yottorana on …ìee won…ìe on tampinde tampere,  
\v 7 e ka o ye…óa on …ìuttu, onon tampinaa…ìe …ìen, wondude e amen, nde Iisaa Joomi on fee…≤oyi ka kammu, wondude e malaa'ikaa…ìe dolnu…ìe …ìen  
\v 8 e hakkunde joyngol yiite, fii yaggingol …ìe andaa Alla …ìen e …ìe …óoftanooki Kibaaru Mo∆¥∆¥o Iisaa Joomi men on.  
\v 9 ∆Åe lettiree halakuyee poomayankeejo, …ìe wo…ó…óitoo Joomi on e mangu bawgal makko ngal  
\v 10 nde o aroyi e nden …≤alaande, fii yo o darjine immorde e laa…ìu…ìe makko …ìen, o mugina gom…óin…ìe …ìen fow. Onon kadi, on gom…óinii ko men seeditanii on kon.  
\v 11 Ko …óun wa…ói, me…óen duumaade e toranagol on, fii no Alla men on wa…óira on rin…óan…ìe ngurndan …óan o noddiri on …óan, e no o laatinira e mon kala e…ì…ìooje mo∆¥∆¥e e kuu…óe gom…óinal mon ngal tippude e bawgal makko ngal,  
\v 12 fii no innde Iisaa Joomi men on mawniniree e mon, e no onon kadi mawninire…óon e makko, sabu sulfu Alla men on e Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi on. 
\c 2  
\s1 Fii Aaden Bon…óo on 
\p  
\v 1 Fii ardu Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi on, e mottondiral men ngal e makko, men torike on, yo musi…ì…ìe,  
\v 2 wota on ja…ìu …ìer…óe mon yaawee jii…ìeede, maa aaninire…óon wi'ugol …≤alaande Joomi on hewtii. Hay si go…ó…óo wi'ii on ko Alla longini men maa ko nelal maa ko …ìatakuru ko iwri e amen, wota on hulu.  
\v 3 Wota hay gooto faljinir on noone woo, ko fii nden …≤alaande arataa ado murtaldu ndun wa…óude, e fee…≤ugol aaden bon…óo on, on muuyanaa…óo hayrugol,  
\v 4 …óun ko on dartotoo…óo immoo daroo e hoore kala ko ne…ó…óanke inni ko alla e hoore kala ko rewetee, o yaha haa o joo…óoyoo ka juulirde Alla mawnde, o wi'itoo kanko tigi Alla. 
\p  
\v 5 On anditaali mi…óo wowlanaynoo on …óun, wa fewndo ko mi wondi e mon?  
\v 6 Jooni non hi…óon andi tigi ko tongi mo, fii yo o fee…≤u e saa'i makko on,  
\v 7 ko fii fewndo …óoo, doole bon…óe suu…óii…óe …óen no gollude, ko woni tun fewndo …óoo go…ó…óo no ha…ói …óe taho haa o dira.  
\v 8 Ko onsay non aaden bon…óo on fee…≤ata. Iisaa Joomi on muliray mo wuttugol, o muncira mo jalbeendi ardu makko ndun kanko Iisaa.  
\v 9 On aaden bon…óo ardoyay e kuu…óe Ibuliisa, o wa…óa noone kaawakeeji e maandeeji e kuu…óe fenaandeeje,  
\v 10 o huutoray kala noone bone fii faayingol won…ìe mulude …ìen, …ìay …ìe ja…ìaali yi…óude goonga on fii no …ìe dandiree.  
\v 11 Ko …óun wa…ói si Alla kadi accidi …ìe e doole …óaynooje fii no …ìe gom…óinira fenaande nden,  
\v 12 fii no yi…óu…ìe angal peewal ngal, gom…óinaali goonga on …ìen …≤aawiree. 
\s1 Fii Tabital …ìe Tesalonii …ìen 
\p  
\v 13 Telen-ma amen menen, yo musi…ì…ìe …ìe Joomiraa…óo on yi…ói, me…óen haani duumaade e jarnugol Alla fii mon, ko fii Allaahu on su…ìino on gila ka fu…ó…óoode fii kisiyee on\f a \fr 2:13 \ft 2.13 \+it Maa: \+it* ko fii Allaahu on su…ìorno on wa dikkuruu…ìe fii kisiyee on.\f*, e hoore *la…ì…ìinirgol on Ruuhu Allaahu on e gom…óingol goonga on.  
\v 14 Ko …óun o noddiri on Kibaaru Mo∆¥∆¥o mo men fe…≤…≤inani on on, fii no he…ìiron ge…ìal ka mangu Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi on.  
\v 15 Ko …óun wa…ói, yo musi…ì…ìe, wonee tabitu…ìe, jogito…óon janndeeji …ói men janni on …óin, woni non ko e kongu…ói, woni e …ìataake.  
\v 16 Yo Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi men on tigi, e Alla Baaba men, on Yi…óu…óo en, ye…ói en wakkilaare poomayankeere e tama'u mo∆¥∆¥o immorde e sulfu makko on,  
\v 17 wakkilin …ìer…óe mon …óen, tabintina on e kala kuugal e kala kongol mo∆¥∆¥ol. 
\c 3  
\s1 Puulusa Landii …ìe Tesalonii …ìen Torndeeji 
\p  
\v 1 Ka rawnoode, yo musi…ì…ìe, toranee men fii no daaluyee Joomiraa…óo on lollira e no mawniniree, wano o lolliri e mawniri ka mon non,  
\v 2 fii no men dandiree …ìoylii…ìe …ìen e bon…ìe …ìen, ko fii hinaa fow mari gom…óinal.  
\v 3 Kono Joomiraa…óo on ko Sella-Findeejo, o tabintinay on, o hisina on bon…óo on.  
\v 4 Joomiraa…óo on no okki men hoolaare e telen-ma mon wonde hi…óon wa…óude, on wa…óoyay kadi ko men yamiri on kon.  
\v 5 Yo Joomiraa…óo on ardo …ìer…óe mon …óen e fee giggol iwrungol e Alla e ≈ãa…≤…≤aare iwrunde e *Almasiihu on. 
\s1 Hajannde fii Puyndan 
\p  
\v 6 Men yamirii on e innde Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi men on, yo musi…ì…ìe, yo on wo…ó…óito kala musi…ó…óo wuuru…óo e nder puyndan, ko yaadaa e jannde nde hendor…óon men nden.  
\v 7 Ko fii hi…óon andi onon tigi ko honno …≤embirton men, ko fii men wuuriraali puyndan hakkunde mon.  
\v 8 Men ja…ìaali go…ó…óo fawtoo men …≤aametee nii tun, kono ko e nder golle sattu…óe e yangi men golliri jemma e …≤alorma, fii wota men wonan hay gooto e mon dongal.  
\v 9 Wonaa fii hari …óun no haanani men men wa…óiri …óun, kono men faalano on accirde menen tigi noone mo …≤embon.  
\v 10 E hoore …óun, fewndo ko men wonnoo ka mon, men wa…óanno on ndee yamiroore …óoo: kala on salii…óo gollude, wota …≤aamu kadi! 
\p  
\v 11 E hin-le men nanii wo…ì…ìe e hakkunde mon no jokki puyndan, hi…ìe jokki ko wonaa haaju ma…ì…ìe edii …ìe gollude.  
\v 12 Men torike …ìen yim…ìe, men jeejirii …ìe Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi on, yo …ìe gollu e nder …ìuttu, …ìe …≤aama ko …ìe to'ani hoore ma…ì…ìe kon.  
\v 13 Onon non, yo musi…ì…ìe, wota …ìer…óe mon maayan wa…óugol ko mo∆¥∆¥i. 
\p  
\v 14 On mo …óoftaaki ko men wi'i kon e nduu …ìatakuru, haray maandinee fii makko. Wota on huuwondir e makko huuwondiral woo, fii yo o hersu.  
\v 15 Wota on jogor mo non wa ga…≤o, kono hajoree mo wa musi…ó…óo mon. 
\s1 Fii Waynitannde nden 
\p  
\v 16 Yo Joomiraa…óo, Jom ∆Åuttu on, ye…óu on …ìuttu kanko tigi saa'i kala e noone kala. Yo Joomiraa…óo on wondu e mon on fow. 
\p  
\v 17 Min Puulusa, mi salminirii on jungo an ngon tigi. Ko maande an nden woni e nder …ìataake an …óen fow, e hino bindi an …óin.  
\v 18 Yo mo∆¥∆¥ere Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi men on wonu e mon on fow.